{"tid":670082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"洗牙補牙杜牙根問題","createTime":"2018-05-19T05:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T03:54:19.000Z","uid":181719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"275f3aac438a232d67c4cdedd175b5f15d29f0a5","tid":670082,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:01:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，平時冇牙痛食野亦冇問題，只係記起好耐冇洗過牙，聽個長輩介紹去睇個牙醫，本來話基本洗牙420。<br />\n<br />\n去到洗，牙醫話我刷牙太大力，磨蝕哂牙肉，呢個我知道嘅最近刷牙都盡量細力咗，但問題黎喇，佢話我左上左下右上右下 4 part 牙都有好多要補+杜牙根。補就一堆，杜牙根4至5隻，加加埋埋5皮野冇走雞。<br />\n<br />\n最後淨係補咗右上part三隻，加洗牙，已經1720......<br />\n<br />\n想問各位巴打有冇類似經歷？即係生活冇問題但洗牙果陣講到你棚牙就爛哂咁？可信性有幾高？或者有咩相熟牙醫推介？感激不盡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f06cdcf852bd36d6a5ad8ad34eba0248b48714","tid":670082,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:02:13.000Z","msg":"你幾耐洗一次？"},{"pid":"4faef8b171b11b3849db29345635eb42a9af185a","tid":670082,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53f06cdcf852bd36d6a5ad8ad34eba0248b48714","tid":670082,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:02:13.000Z","msg":"你幾耐洗一次？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:03:31.000Z","msg":"原來好耐無洗 一年洗一次啦"},{"pid":"0c7b0f5f38f18d1c8044e1224fe18ab417abad6e","tid":670082,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa6ff010709160cfa81e9582b69e1ad6f6e54de3","tid":670082,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"53f06cdcf852bd36d6a5ad8ad34eba0248b48714","tid":670082,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:02:13.000Z","msg":"你幾耐洗一次？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"五年以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實依家就係諗住下年搵第二個洗，再睇吓會唔會有唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b695e469e70b7565d8f6d90a0bc4c0b82010c0d","tid":67